snippet.title: Guardian by Alligata Software C64 gameplay.
snippet.description:
I didn't see this game videod on YT and what a crime, this is a beautiful version of Defender as you can see. My skills don't do this game any justice but I still like playing this game anyway.

Couldn't remember the key for the smartbomb in my impatience!! :o)

Enjoy.
